node.text: What a treat Sheryl❤️😍 love it

💗A platter of delightful kuehs from @harrianns 💗 Now which one’s your favourite. I usually attack the kueh salat and the ondeh ondeh first followed by the kueh rainbow lapis 😋

Craving for kuehs? Do check out @harrianns Facebook page for more of their yummy offerings this CB!

@mountainsofmeals hehehe Glad it did! Happy weekend 💋
What a delightful platter you're right
@olgazapisek hahhaa totally love your imagination!!! How have u been friend!!

@sherbakes I have a photo and caption ready to go, just need to pick a day— either today or tomorrow to post 🤣. Other than that, busy growing my business, and just trying not to get cabin fever 🙂. How about you? How’s the weekend treating you? Staying home or venturing out a little bit?
@sherbakes and I love your imagination as well, girl! ❤️
Am i the only one who is tempted to play with those cubes and build something like you would with LEGOs? Who says we can’t play with our food ❤️🙌🏻.
What a treat Sheryl❤️😍 love it
